data.description: Welcome to this captivating sprawling ranch (with a partial basement) nestled in the prestigious Flossmoor Estates, boasting 3,315 square feet of luxurious living space. Conveniently located near the Metra, historic downtown Flossmoor, and the esteemed Western Avenue School, this residence offers the perfect blend of convenience and charm.     As you approach, the grandeur of the home is immediately evident with its large front covered porch, providing an inviting entrance. Step inside the elegant foyer that sets the tone for the rest of the home, leading you to the spacious living room adorned with a classic fireplace and formal dining room featuring hardwood flooring throughout.     The kitchen is a chef's delight, showcasing a harmonious combination of white and quartz countertops, exposed brick, a farmhouse sink, marble splash, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The culinary experience is enhanced by double ovens and a built-in granite table, creating a perfect space for family gatherings and entertaining. French doors open to a deck, seamlessly connecting indoor and outdoor living.    The heart of the home is the expansive family room, featuring a vaulted ceiling, another fireplace, and a cozy den area. This inviting space provides the perfect backdrop for relaxation and entertainment.    Retreat to the enormous primary bedroom suite, complete with doors leading to a private office or exercise room. Three additional generous bedrooms offer ample space for family and guests. The thoughtful layout and design of this home provide both comfort and functionality.    With its prime location and impressive features, this ranch-style residence in Flossmoor Estates offers a unique opportunity for those seeking a harmonious blend of modern luxury and timeless charm. Don't miss the chance to make this house your dream home!
